rComments: He is one of the best profs on the UTM campus
Extremely helpful, crystal clear explanation, and very approachable. Basically one of, if not the best instructor I've ever met in my first two years in university. That final exam though...

One of the best profs I've ever had! Answers your questions in class and makes sure everyone's on the same page before moving on. He's animated and engaging and uses simple language to reword theorems to help you understand. If only he was teaching my other math courses too...
Great personality! Best Math professor I've ever had. Explained concepts really well. Always make sure everyone understands it. He is a singer and improviser,too!
Amazing prof! Could explain concepts so clearly. Always ensured all of his students understood the material. Best math teacher I've ever had!
